292
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:44,800
Yujin Tea.

293
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,920
Luya Tea.

294
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:49,920
Right, right.

295
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:52,400
Five-fruit Drink.

296
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,480
Sweet Pastry.

297
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:59,440
And your Stewed Pear.

298
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,040
