300
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:03,320
Good.

301
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:04,680
You missed nothing.

302
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:06,920
Sanniang,

303
00:17:07,800 --> 00:17:10,350
