355
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,960
Sanniang, would you like to...

356
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,000
Sit down and enjoy your tea!

357
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:14,640
Come out!

358
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:17,360
