to keep walking.

447
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:47,080
May I have some porridge?

448
00:22:47,600 --> 00:22:49,080
But we don't eat boiled food here.

449
00:22:49,360 --> 00:22:50,480
Sorry for that.

450
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:05,600
Sorry, Mr. Ouyang.

451
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:07,440
